Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A secret passage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,a hidden room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:13.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They were all prepared by Professor Pavlichenko to hide the existence of his son,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:16.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and to escape in case of an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are also traces of tampering in the family registry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:22.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And not only once, but twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:26.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he go that far to hide his son?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:31.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's related to his research that he's been secretly conducting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:36.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that ME network drivel mentioned in the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:41.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If that was feasible, we would both be jobless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:45.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are pieces missing everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:48.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was the case with Professor Pavlichenko's corpse, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:54.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The DNA proves that the body was indeed his.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:01:01.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But the ME squeezer was only able to extract a day's worth of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:08.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Were both analyses wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:09.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We got this a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:16.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's from an SVR agent in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:19.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This was taken 26 hours ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:23.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In Tokyo.
