Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.65,DTB-Notes,,0,0,0,,Ishizaka Kanami - Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be in the archives,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,yet you are here in this creepy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:26.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wasn't this place the hive of the dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for Izanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At least you were discrete enough not to call your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:39.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The lines are obviously tapped, and would cause that person a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And you might be able to notice now that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,you're already being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:46.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A surveillance spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:50.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky there aren't any power lines here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:55.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We took all the know-how after the astronomy division was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And now we've got Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are they planning anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:09.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A grunt like me won't be informed of anything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:14.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what the higher-ups are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So? Wanna partner up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do you have the Japanese Public Safety on your ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:27.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but the CIA which you betrayed and the Russian organization, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:31.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy to get out of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A transporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They'll help if we pay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with an informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We do business if we both have common goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's not a nice way to greet people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're 200m ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's an inspection ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take a different route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:40.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:47.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If they are checking this place too, I don't think there's another way out of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:51.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure they have covered every path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:56.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to think this thoroughly before we get to Hakodate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That has its price too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:06.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There were some deviations in the plan, but we've managed to get Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:10.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, they tried to kill Izanami, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It looked that way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:19.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're still investigating who's behind this and where the information was leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:30.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Izanami's father is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As expected. You've already heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to drink it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So far, we've only received information that we found a matching person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're still investigating that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:52.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The time stated in the Mitaka documents isn't that far in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,While there's no moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ikuta's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How is your family doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll contact you again when I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet at the usual place, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How about a tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll boost up your manliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need a photo to plaster on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see you rented another strange car again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dolls are unexpectedly easy to distinguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The blizzard is still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm stuck here in Sapporo because of a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:09.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's a car or a train, just get me to Tokyo immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet train isn't working either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should take an express train?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Though, there's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The people out there don't give shit about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is this little lady a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:30.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We use the contractors that are trained in your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't from the consulate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're from foreign affairs. Their allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about that incident in Sapporo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:46.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't heard anything. Not even which organizations were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:50.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,According to our investigations, we believe a Japanese agency is involved in that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:54.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But we have received this from an eyewitness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:04.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We believe it's the doll and the girl that were mentioned in the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:07.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:10.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can most likely find our target if we watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a skilled contractor to mark them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ilya Sokolov. I think you've heard of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's indeed skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:25.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So much that he sickens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When you speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We just got information regarding a smuggling route for dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't eating that ice cream making you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:44.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? You just wolfed down all those dishes earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A white guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can you speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What were you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The remains of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He met with an unfortunate accident while he was on a trip to Aomori by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And his family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:57.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His father and sister are in the car behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look in the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eight and ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I've taken you to Sendai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:26.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll board the Cassiopeia at 04:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I think they won't be thoroughly monitoring at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried you can switch trains at the local station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we take July out for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be inspections at Aomori too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so it'll be a hassle to get him back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:53.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely being alone in this coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should speak up if something is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:40.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A flat tire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:53.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the doll business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:59.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So she was after July from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we chase after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chase? For July?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:07.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You got attached to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I need him when I use my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so cold toward July?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's merely a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:26.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But in Yin's case, you acted so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:34.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,With your powers gone, you will need her-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we don't know where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:44.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's July's surveillance spirit. He's asking for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:52.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't take my eyes off of you for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.55,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode 7    The Doll Sings to the Dancing Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was teasing July a bit earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:11.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't really tell how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he's a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But he's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise he wouldn't have sent that surveillance spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:30.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}I'm sure the fragments of our hearts won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of if we're dolls or contractors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mao, we'll get off at the next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get onto another car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Little boys as dolls are pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can get in from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go scout that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you the professional here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, missus slave driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,More like an animal driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Understand your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Almost anything can be used as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:32.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get her away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that by making some noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but are you planning to go in with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I use my rifle, the police could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking rationally, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:09.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:30.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to rescue July!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous if some amateurs try to deal with dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Every country wants a skilled doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:04.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so doll smugglers are always in touch with intelligence agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:14.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an opiate for the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your pain fades away; you feel sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you stop breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a contractor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:09.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is this squirrel a contractor too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Squirrel? I'm a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:23.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't follow, July.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those who're killed by me are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They die dreaming of something pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:43.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since you've stopped dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:46.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you how long you've been a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still not aware of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:57.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really saved by not being able to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:01.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I used to often dream of the women I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I murdered them in atrocious ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The complete opposite of how I'm killing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed watching their suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:20.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing that from an animal is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's all pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or better said I've stopped killing them in an irrational way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:31.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it anymore, because I've become a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that ironic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just die like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:37.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call the informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:41.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that a bad idea? Especially in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:42.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to thank someone, thank July.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? Hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A bump?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:54.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:17.77,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:17.77,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:28.28,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:28.28,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:37.84,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:37.84,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:44.02,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:44.02,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.77,0:22:49.12,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.77,0:22:49.12,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.75,0:22:53.88,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.75,0:22:53.88,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.65,0:23:02.53,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.65,0:23:02.53,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:02.35,0:23:07.62,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:23:02.35,0:23:07.62,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:07.36,0:23:14.57,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:07.36,0:23:14.57,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:14.20,0:23:22.16,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:14.20,0:23:22.16,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:22.08,0:23:32.45,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:22.08,0:23:32.45,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake already?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:40.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:46.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,For hunting, you have to get to the spot early to camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:04.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the glitter of that summer day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:07.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The sunlight making its way into the room through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:10.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The spray of water trickling down your blond hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The echoes through the cold wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A distant memory of laughter. The fault of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:20.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A memory takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:24.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The silver train runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:28.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then... we cannot go back to that day.